      • separate

        public List<ChunkedList<T>> separate(int n)
        Seperates the contents of the ChunkedList in n parts. This can be used to apply a forEach method in parallel using 'n' threads for instance. The method returns n lists, each containing a ChunkedList of Ts.
        Parameters:
        n - the number of parts in which to split the ChunkedList
        Returns:
        n ChunkedLists containing the same number of elements
